@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/_layout.css" asp-append-version="true"/>

<section class="container text-white py-4">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Welcome to <strong>iReadIt</strong>! Your privacy is important to us, and this policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, and other details for account creation.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Buying and Borrowing history and preferences to enhance recommendations.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> For subscriptions or purchases (if applicable).</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Cookies, IP address, and analytics data to improve the platform.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Manage your account and provide library services.</li>
        <li>Enhance your experience with personalized recommendations.</li>
        <li>Process payments securely (if applicable).</li>
        <li>Analyze usage to improve platform performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. However, we may share your data with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Service providers for payment processing or technical support.</li>
        <li>Legal authorities if required by law.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard measures to protect your data, including encryption and secure servers. However, we encourage you to use strong passwords and remain vigilant.</p>

    <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to improve your experience and gather usage data. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data collection or usage.</li>
        <li>Contact us to exercise these rights.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes through the website or via email.</p>

    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@ireadit.com" class="text-info">support@ireadit.com</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-4">Effective Date: <strong>December 4, 2024</strong></p>
</section>
